      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and finely chop the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>leek<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>in half lengthways, then wash to remove any grit from between the leaves</p><p>Top, tail and slice finely</p><p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>potatoes</strong></p>",
